svoja mesta? -Da, da.

24
00:02:39,868 --> 00:02:41,537
Vidimo se na zabavi.

25
00:02:42,621 --> 00:02:47,209
Možete li naći gospodina Barria i
podsetiti ga da se izvodi njegovo

26
00:02:48,085 --> 00:02:49,086
Da, gospođo. - Hvala.

27
00:03:29,585 --> 00:03:31,128
LONDON, 1903

28
00:03:33,881 --> 00:03:36,008
lNSPlRlSANO lSTlNlTlM DOGAŠAJEM

29
00:04:04,995 --> 00:04:06,413
Gospodine...

30
00:04:07,372 --> 00:04:09,166
Gospođa Barrie je želela
da vas podsetim da...

31
00:04:09,625 --> 00:04:12,169
